261
00:19:57,397 --> 00:20:00,264
<i>¿Tenemos que pertenecer
a un club?</i>

262
00:20:02,502 --> 00:20:04,354
K.P.S. GILL, IPS (RETIRADO)

263
00:20:04,404 --> 00:20:06,395
ENCARGADO
